Download Haskell with "pacman -S stack ghc"

Compile file with 
  stack exec -- ghc [inputFile].hs -o [outputFile].hs
Execute file with
  ./[outputFile]
  
  
  
  Tutorials / Talks
    https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1jZ7j21g028
    
  Example websites
    https://www.schoolofhaskell.com/school/to-infinity-and-beyond/pick-of-the-week/Simple%20examples
